snippet.title: Minecraft Halloween Mash-Up Pack
snippet.description:
Boo! It´s that time of year when ghouls and ghosts haunt your Minecraft creations.  The Halloween Mash-up pack includes 43 terrifying character skins - vampires, mad scientists and other creepy crawlers. You´ll find a brand new world full of scary blocks and an eerie soundtrack that will make your heart skip a beat. 
So don´t be afraid and build your spooky worlds. 
Minecraft Halloween Mash-up is available October 23, 2015.
